                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17820911-125-off614 t17820911-125-cd615"></join>, a silver<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="178209110121"></xptr> watch, value 40 s. a base metal watch-chain, value 2 d. and a key, value 1 d.
            </rs> the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t17820911-125-victim1243" type="victimName">
                     Richard 
                     Coverly
                  <interp inst="t17820911-125-victim1243" type="surname" value="Coverly"></interp>
